    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "Erm my Hibernate distribution doesn&#39;t have this class... It seems to have been added in the nearer past.  The use case I have is a bug that I can&#39;t figure out: see <a href=\"http://forum.hibernate.org/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=1006411\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">forum.hibernate.org/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=1006411</a>  This is because I use embedded JBoss on Tomcat and this distribution comes with Hibernate whose version I don&#39;t know. Chances are a newer version could resolve the issue (I posted a link to a bug report)."
