    "question_id" : 3480608,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This simple Java code is get the Hibernate version.</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>package com.test;\npublic class HibernateVersion {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        try {\n            String hv = org.hibernate.Version.getVersionString();\n            System.out.println(&quot;Hibernate Version: &quot; + hv);\n        } catch (Exception e) {\n            e.printStackTrace();\n        }\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Output:</strong> <code>Hibernate Version: 6.6.22.Final</code></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3155243,
